sourcesContent: /* eslint-disable no-unused-vars */ import React, { memo } from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' import { Grid, Skeleton } from '../../../components' import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'; import { faCheck } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'; import Card from './Card' function Board({ data }) { const { cases, todayDeaths, recovered, deaths, todayCases } = data const getValue = (value) => value ? value : return ( ) } export default memo(Board)
